title: ST_GEOGPOINTFROMGEOHASH | Snowflake Documentation
paragraphs:
Returns a GEOGRAPHY object for the Point that represents the center of a
geohash.
The argument must be a geohash.

The function returns a value of type GEOGRAPHY that represents the Point that is
the center of the geohash.
